Star Rover 2 - Installation
===========================

Where to get the source

The source is available at http://github.com/anttisalonen/starrover2.
It should also be available at Hackage (http://hackage.haskell.org/) by
the time you read this.

To install from Hackage, you need cabal (Common Architecture for Building 
Applications and Libraries, http://www.haskell.org/cabal/).


To install from Hackage, do:

cabal update && cabal install starrover2


To install from source, you need to have GHC (Glasgow Haskell Compiler)
as well as cabal.

To install from source user-wide, do:

cabal configure --user
cabal build
cabal install

Make sure you have $HOME/.cabal/bin in your $PATH.

To install system-wide, do:

cabal configure
cabal build
cabal install


To run, type in:

starrover2


